title: Looking for Mid/Top/Jungle for Eclipse
body:
Hi all!

Adc for Eclipse here, we're a Bronze/Silver ranked team looking for some people to fill out the last few roles.

Feel free to add me in game or on Skype if you are interested!

IGN: LetsTwitch (Skype is the same)

replies.body: what rank are you? Im Silver 1 top main.

Hey! I am a pref mid lane, and can also jungle if needed. Add me on league and send me a message.
I haven't joined a team before and  would love to see how it goes ^^
im a jungle main, can also top lane. hardcore yi main. and i win games. wouldnt mind trying something different and joining a team ~
